# WalletConnect/Reown project ID — this is a public client identifier (not a
# secret), so a real value is committed here rather than left blank. The
# same value is also already baked in as the default in src/lib/wagmi.ts, so
# the app works even without this file being copied to .env. Override here
# (or in Vercel's project environment variables) only if you want to use a
# different WalletConnect project — get one at https://cloud.reown.com.
VITE_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=a0031066837361c93d02ae2f139acc98

# Populated after BuilderPassport.sol is deployed to GIWA Sepolia (Milestone 3).
# Optional — src/lib/contract.ts already defaults to the Milestone 2 Remix
# deployment (0x36Dae8dCFf051f301D5e02a37d203b9f7DB93142). Set this only to
# override that default, e.g. once a future redeploy replaces it.
VITE_BUILDER_PASSPORT_ADDRESS=
